metadata.name: Mary 003
metadata.description:
She is Liz's older sister. Her name is Mary. She is 24 years old. She is a musician like her sister. She often plays the violin to rest her sister's soul, who is looking for an outlet. She calms her down with the melodies she creates. Even though the Corona virus separates them with masks, more united their worlds inside.

It is very difficult to find morale in the days of the epidemic. However, talented families can easily achieve this. Mary thinks she is in a war. She knows that she will destroy this evil with the power of art. She plays the violin for both her family and the world. Thus, she is sure that all wars and epidemics will end.

Dimensions:  4500× 3612 
Resolution: 300 dpi
Edition: 1/1
Taken/Edit: 2021

16 photos and true stories from the lives of 16 people.
Number 003 in the series: Mary
The stories are real. Names and photos are fictitious.
Artist name: Berker Dalmis
